      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dents, with some areas of faded or worn paint. The interior shows moderate wear including worn upholstery and some scuffed trim panels. Mechanically functional, but cosmetic issues are present throughout.",
      "price": 16500.0,
